== .crush DSL

  target :test do
    uri 'http://www.test.com'
  end
  
  scenario :normal do
  
    duration 300 # seconds
    
    launch 5, 'test.com-user' do |target, scenario, options, job_id| do
      WebUser.new(...).start!
    end
    
    launch 1, 'test.com-admin' do |target, scenario, options, job_id| do
      WebUser.new(...).start!
    end
  
  end

== crush executable

Reads .crush in CWD for targets and scenarios, invoke like this:

  crush target_name scenario_name [log_file]

